        <item>
            <title>网民实践用 ChatGPT 制实体公仔，自创 5 个步骤由生成公仔草图到 3D 列印</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/14/chatgpt-figure/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=chatgpt-figure</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/14/chatgpt-figure/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 14 Apr 2025 11:24:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303246</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>生成式 AI 技术席卷创作界，不少网民都用 ChatGPT 来制作吉卜力图片，有些网民就爱用 GPT 来生成「公仔」。但好多网民都是生成公仔「图片」来玩玩便算，而近日就有一位网民实践将 ChatGPT 结合 3D 模型技术，以极为便捷的方法，制作出一系列个人化公仔，不但造型细致生动，AI、3D 打印的辅助下整个制作流程大幅提速，引起网民热议。这位网民的例子展示 AI 辅助创作在实体制品上的潜力，实现从构思、绘图、建模至列印的完整流程。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472116.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303265" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472116-681x580.jpg" alt="" width="681" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472116-681x580.jpg 681w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472116.jpg 1057w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 681px" /></a></p><p>这位名为「Model work」的网民在 Facebook 专页「ChatGPT 4o + Copilot and ALL AI 生成式艺术小小咏唱师」发文，详细分享其创作过程，强调 GPT 模型强大之处，令公仔设计不再困难，只需简单五个步骤即可完成 3D 成品。他的创意与执行力，获得众多网民赞赏。以下为他的五大关键流程解析：</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490346772_1221334695.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490346772_1221334695-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490346772_1221334695-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490346772_1221334695.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a></p><p>一、用 ChatGPT 协助生成图像构想</p><p>他以 ChatGPT 作为起点，输入想要的角色风格与主题，由 GPT 协助生成角色外观草图或描述，作为创作原型。这一步骤大幅减轻绘图负担，对无插画经验者尤为有用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490420347_1221334695.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303254 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490420347_1221334695-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490420347_1221334695-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490420347_1221334695.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p>二、利用 Tripo3D 将图像转化为初步 3D 模型</p><p>接著，他透过 Tripo3D 工具快速将 2D 概念图转换成 3D 模型，实现初步的立体化，缩短建模准备时间。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490385309_1221334764.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303255" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490385309_1221334764-518x580.jpg" alt="" width="518" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490385309_1221334764-518x580.jpg 518w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490385309_1221334764.jpg 803w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 518px" /></a></p><p>三、Zbrush 精修与分件，输出 STL 档案<br />
为让模型更具细节与可列印性，他将 Tripo3D 的模型导入专业雕刻工具 Zbrush，进行精修与分件，再输出 STL 档案作为 3D 列印的标准格式。</p><p>四、使用赤兔切片软件进行支撑设置</p><p>STL 档输出后，他选用「赤兔」切片软件（Chitubox 类型工具）进行模型切片与支撑架设，确保列印过程中模型不会变形或倒塌。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490113881_1221334695.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303256" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490113881_1221334695-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490113881_1221334695-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490113881_1221334695.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490063517_1221334695.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303257" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490063517_1221334695-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490063517_1221334695-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490063517_1221334695.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a></p><p>五、进行 3D 列印并上色</p><p>最后进行实体列印，他展示多个完成品，包括戴口罩吃泡面公仔、骑机车角色、戴耳机公仔等，动作与神情极具个性，更成功上色还原插画风格。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490704421_1221334764.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303258" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490704421_1221334764-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490704421_1221334764-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490704421_1221334764.jpg 720w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490111783_1221334695.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303259" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490111783_1221334695-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490111783_1221334695-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490111783_1221334695.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490418580_1221334695.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303260" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490418580_1221334695-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490418580_1221334695-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/490418580_1221334695.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a></p><p>不少网民看完后纷纷留言赞叹这套流程「直接把玩具工厂搬进家」，也有人提到「上色先最难，ChatGPT 都帮唔到手」，但亦有留言者回应指出，目前若使用如 Tripo3D、Hi3D、Luma 等进阶工具，其实已可生成全彩模型，只要配合全彩 3D 列印机便可省却手动上色。</p><p>还有网民更直言：「所以可以轻松客制化公仔了」，点出这项流程的商业潜力与普及前景。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_312-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303253" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_312-1-694x212.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="212" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_312-1-694x212.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_312-1.jpg 1232w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_312.jpg"><br /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_212.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_212-694x406.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="406" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_212-694x406.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250414_6_59_212.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>透过 AI 结合 3D 技术，这位创作者不仅展示出个人创意，更示范出新一代创作人如何活用科技工具改变传统创作流程。此例子亦为未来 3D 公仔客制化市场提供极具参考价值的实践模式。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472323.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1303266" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472323-486x580.jpg" alt="" width="486" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472323-486x580.jpg 486w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041472323.jpg 754w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 486px" /></a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/592850912909945/search/?q=GPT%20%E5%BE%88%E7%8C%9B%EF%BC%8C">Facebook</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/14/chatgpt-figure/ai/">网民实践用 ChatGPT 制实体公仔，自创 5 个步骤由生成公仔草图到 3D 列印</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
